These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, november, june, march
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, basketball, biathlon, rowing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, ambient, r&b, d&b
1. the fan of country is the person who's birthday is in march##1
2. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
5. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
6. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
7. the fan of ambient is on the far left or far right##3
8. the fan of d&b is between the person who's sport is rowing and the person who's birthday is in august##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Birthday         | march      | august | november | june |
| Sport   | biathlon | cricket  | basketball   | rowing    |
| Music-Genre     | country     | r&b    | d&b    | ambient      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
City: marseilles, paris, miami, edinburgh
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, grapes, pepper, pear
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, water, cola, sprite
1. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person traveling to miami##3
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person eating pepper##1
3. the person traveling to miami is in an even position##4
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1
6. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
7. the person eating cabbage is between the person traveling to edinburgh and the person traveling to paris##2
8. the person eating pear is between the person eating grapes and the person traveling to miami##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| City         | edinburgh | miami   | paris | marseilles  |
| Food   | pepper     | cabbage | pear  | grapes |
| Beverage     | sprite        | cola  | water    | mirinda |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, havana, siglo, pall-mall
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, skiing, cricket, baseball
There are 4 different favourite colors: yellow, mauve, turquise, lilac
1. the person who's sport is baseball is between the dannemann-smoker and the pall-mall-smoker##2
2. the person who's sport is skiing is the person who likes lilac##1
3. the person who likes yellow is the siglo-smoker##1
4. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
5. the pall-mall-smoker is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is cricket is between the havana-smoker and the person who's sport is lacrosse##2
7. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Cigar          | dannemann | havana   | pall-mall     | siglo     |
| Sport   | skiing  | baseball | cricket   | lacrosse  |
| Color     | lilac      | mauve | turquise | yellow |

