.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, aconite, begonia, rose
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, soy-milk, tea, mirinda
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, montecristo, blend, ritmeester
1. the person drinking mirinda is in an even position##4
2. the person who growsaconite is the montecristo-smoker##1
3. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person who growsbegonia##3
5. the person drinking mirinda is the davidoff-smoker##1
6. the person who growsbegonia is the person drinking 7up##1
7. the person drinking tea is the person who growsorchid##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Flower   | orchid  | rose   | begonia     | aconite |
| Beverage   | tea  | mirinda      | 7up        | soy-milk     |
| Cigar         | blend | davidoff | ritmeester | montecristo   |

