.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
4 different games are played: chess, go, whist, monopoly
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, paramedic, architect, dressmaker
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, martial-arts, horror, documentary
1. the person playing monopoly is the dressmaker##1
2. the person playing whist is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching thriller movies is the dressmaker##1
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the dressmaker##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is in an even position##4
6. the paramedic is on the far left##1
7. the person playing go is on the far right##1
8. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
9. the fisherman is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Game   | chess   | monopoly   | whist | go |
| Job         | paramedic      | dressmaker | fisherman      | architect |
| Movie-Genre     | martial-arts | thriller        | documentary       | horror  |

