.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
House: modern, palace, gothic-revival, cape-cod
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, coffee, lemonade, sprite
The people have 4 different jobs:  writer, nurse, journalist, videographer
1. the palace house is in an odd position##4
2. the journalist is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the writer is the palace house##1
4. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the nurse##1
5. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1
6. the cape-cod house is on the left of the palace house##1
7. the cape-cod house is in an even position##4
8. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| House    | gothic-revival   | cape-cod      | palace       | modern |
| Beverage   | juice | sprite | lemonade     | coffee |
| Job     | videographer     | nurse  | writer | journalist |

