.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, colombian, nigerian, brazilian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, ice-hockey, golf, baseball
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, hip-hop, house, classical
1. the fan of house is the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is between the person who's sport is baseball and the fan of blues##2
3. the person who's sport is baseball is the colombian##1
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the colombian##3
5. the thai is in an even position##4
6. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the brazilian##1
7. the person who's sport is soccer is the thai##1
8. the fan of house is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Nationality      | nigerian   | brazilian          | colombian | thai        |
| Sport   | golf     | ice-hockey | baseball   | soccer     |
| Music-Genre           | blues | hip-hop         | classical         | house |

