.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, billiard, mah-jongg, snooker
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, iced-tea, hot-chocolate
House: cape-cod, colonial, palace, gothic-revival
1. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the palace house##3
2. the person drinking iced-tea is the person playing monopoly##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person playing mah-jongg##1
4. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the palace house##1
5. the colonial house is between the person drinking coffee and the person playing monopoly##2
6. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
7. the person playing monopoly is in an even position##4
8. the person playing monopoly is between the person playing billiard and the person playing mah-jongg##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Game         | billiard | monopoly      | mah-jongg       | snooker    |
| Beverage           | cola  | iced-tea  | hot-chocolate | coffee |
| House   | gothic-revival      | palace | colonial         | cape-cod    |

