.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, japanese, italian, egyptian
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, musical, thriller, spy
4 different games are played: bridge, snooker, billiard, poker
1. the person watching romance movies is in an odd position##4
2. the brazilian is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3
3. the egyptian is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3
4. the person playing snooker is on the left of the brazilian##1
5. the japanese is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
6. the person playing poker is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
7. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the brazilian##1
8. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the italian##1
9. the person watching spy movies is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Nationality   | japanese         | brazilian  | italian     | egyptian         |
| Movie-Genre        | spy | musical | romance | thriller         |
| Game      | snooker         | billiard  | bridge   | poker |

