.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
House: colonial, palace, art-deco, victorian
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, gardening, sudoku, woodworking
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite, water, coffee
 1. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3
 2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the palace house##1
 4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is between the palace house and the colonial house##2
 5. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the palace house##3
 6. the person drinking coffee is the art-deco house##1
 7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far right##1
 8. the colonial house is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the victorian house and the art-deco house##2
10. the person drinking water is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| House   | colonial  | art-deco    | palace | victorian    |
| Hobby   | puzzles | sudoku | gardening  | woodworking |
| Beverage           | water   | coffee    | hot-chocolate        | sprite   |

