.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, fishing, video-games, skydiving
4 different pets are kept: dog, goat, goldfish, cat
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, zombie, fantasy, mystery
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far left or far right##3
2. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
3. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
4. the owner of the goat is in an even position##4
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
6. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
7. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
8. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3
9. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby      | puzzles                | skydiving  | fishing | video-games   |
| Pet           | cat | goat | dog   | goldfish |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie         | adventure     | mystery     | fantasy |

