.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-12::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, prince, vegafina, montecristo
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, goldfish, rabbit, horse
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, dahlia, poppy, daffodil
1. the prince-smoker is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
2. the vegafina-smoker is on the far left##1
3. the person who growsdahlia is on the left or right of the person who growsdaffodil##3
4. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the person who growszinnia is between the owner of the horse and the person who growsdaffodil##2
6. the owner of the rabbit is in an even position##4
7. the dannemann-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Cigar          | vegafina    | prince  | montecristo  | dannemann |
| Pet   | horse | goldfish | guinea-pig | rabbit |
| Flower   | poppy    | zinnia     | daffodil    | dahlia |

