.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, daisy, rose, marigold
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, climbing, parkour, surfing
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, july, april, january
1. the person who's birthday is in july is between the person who growsrose and the person who's sport is soccer##2
2. the person who growstulip is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
5. the person who's birthday is in january is in an odd position##4
6. the person who growsdaisy is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
7. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
8. the person who's sport is parkour is the person who growstulip##1
9. the person who's sport is surfing is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who's birthday is in june##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Flower      | tulip | rose      | daisy  | marigold    |
| Sport   | parkour   | climbing | surfing | soccer |
| Birthday           | january      | april       | july   | june      |

