.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, dog, chinchilla, turtle
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, october, february, august
City: hannover, rome, boston, venice
1. the owner of the chinchilla is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the dog is between the owner of the turtle and the person traveling to hannover##2
3. the person traveling to rome is on the far left or far right##3
4. the owner of the turtle is in an even position##4
5. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
6. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person traveling to hannover and the person who's birthday is in january##2
7. the person traveling to rome is on the far right##1
8. the person who's birthday is in october is in an even position##4
9. the person traveling to hannover is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Pet         | goldfish    | chinchilla | dog  | turtle  |
| Birthday   | february | october       | august | january |
| City         | boston   | hannover      | venice | rome       |

