.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-15::.
4 different games are played: scrabble, whist, billiard, snooker
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, november, july, october
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, boat, motorbike, van
1. the person driving the boat is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the boat is the person playing whist##1
3. the person playing whist is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
4. the person playing billiard is the person who's birthday is in october##1
5. the person playing billiard is on the far left##1
6. the person who's birthday is in december is the person driving the boat##1
7. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
8. the person driving the van is the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |   4    |
| Game      | billiard      | whist | scrabble     | snooker    |
| Birthday   | october | december      | november | july |
| Transport           | motorbike   | boat  | trike     | van |

