.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-16::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, time-travel, sports, martial-arts
4 different pets are kept: goat, rabbit, hamster, horse
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, blood-red, grey, emerald
1. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person watching time-travel movies##3
2. the owner of the goat is in an even position##4
3. the person who likes emerald is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
5. the person watching time-travel movies is between the person who likes blood-red and the owner of the hamster##2
6. the person who likes chestnut is the owner of the horse##1
7. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
8. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre    | sports    | time-travel     | adventure    | martial-arts        |
| Pet       | hamster   | goat | rabbit | horse |
| Color   | emerald | grey      | blood-red    | chestnut   |

