.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-17::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, orange, ivory, ebony
House: futuristic, craftsman, modern, farmhouse
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, writing, filmmaking, chess
1. the craftsman house is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is between the person who's hobby is writing and the person who likes ebony##2
3. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the person who likes ivory##3
4. the person who likes orange is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
6. the person who likes orange is in an odd position##4
7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who likes ebony is the modern house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Color          | orange | ebony  | lavender   | ivory    |
| House   | futuristic  | modern     | farmhouse | craftsman |
| Hobby   | filmmaking   | chess | sudoku | writing   |

