2. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the person eating pomegranate##3
3. the person eating watermelon is on the far left##1
4. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
5. the owner of the goat is the person driving the train##1
6. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
7. the person driving the tram is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
8. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3     |    4     |
| Pet   | frog | fish | goat | turtle   |
| Food   | watermelon    | pomegranate   | pineapple     | potato    |
| Transport   | quad-bike  | tram | train  | motorbike |

