.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, january, december, july
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, skateboard, bus, jet-ski
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, d&b, rock, blues
1. the person who's birthday is in september is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the jet-ski is in an odd position##4
3. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left##1
5. the person who's birthday is in january is between the person driving the jet-ski and the person driving the roller##2
6. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
7. the fan of rock is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
8. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Birthday    | december    | january    | september  | july |
| Transport   | jet-ski | skateboard | roller | bus      |
| Music-Genre     | d&b   | punk        | blues   | rock       |

 